Herbert Henry Edward Scott

Born: 10 Mar 1907, Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia

Marriage (1): May V. Sanderson in 1927 in Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia

Marriage (2): Annie May Glyde in Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia

Died: 7 Apr 1974, Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia at age 67

Another name for Herbert was Bert.

General Notes:

Bert served in the AIF in WW2. Service Number NX36463

Herbert married May V. Sanderson in 1927 in Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia.

Herbert next married Annie May Glyde in 1927 in Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia. (Annie May Glyde was born on 3 Nov 1915 in Hay, New South Wales, Australia and died on 30 Aug 1990 in Narrandera,,New South Wales,Australia.)
